Let's sort out how the discounts work together:1. **Loyalty Points:** To use your loyalty points you first need to go to the 'Benefits' area on our website and convert them into a discount coupon code.2. **Coupon Codes:** Usually you can only use *one* main coupon code per order (like  Amit's code the PASSOVER code or the one you create from your loyalty points). Just note that it is only valid for 3 hours after you receive it and it calculates the 15% discount from the price *after* the main coupon has already been applied.4. **Vouchers (from work):** These are applied separately at the very end on the payment page after you have entered the coupon codes during checkout.So you should be able to use: **One main coupon code** (choose the best one) + **the Spinner discount** (if still valid) + **Your vouchers** (at payment).The problem you saw could be because you tried to apply loyalty points directly without converting them or you tried to use multiple main coupon codes together.
